# Netlify proxy so the static site can call /api/* without CORS issues.
# IMPORTANT: Replace the backend URL below with your deployed backend base URL.
# Example: https://me-to-millets-api.onrender.com

# Favicons: help crawlers that look for /favicon.ico at the site root
/favicon.ico  /images/icons/logo3.png  200
/apple-touch-icon.png  /images/icons/logo3.png  200

# Canonicalize host + scheme
http://metomillets.me/*  https://metomillets.me/:splat  301!
https://www.metomillets.me/*  https://metomillets.me/:splat  301!

/api/*  https://metomillets.onrender.com/api/:splat  200
